name: UI thoughts for NFT based club
description:
The precursor to wireframes. A product owner’s vision. The looks and interface will be guided by these feelings, values, and tenants. An underlying theme is inclusivity thorough ease of use paired with the ability to pull back the curtain and be as dorky as you want. Want to geek with your web 3 friends and count your tokens, we got you. Want to vibe and have a good time without thinking about how it works, no problem. Not just nifty for the sake of nifty, but NFT’s used to create an ecosystem where you may enjoy the moment and build value at the same time. Inclusive UI for different types of people - investors and users.
Ask me more: https://www.linkedin.com/in/ian-aw-ehrlich-mba/
